<p>To enhance the quality of life of local residents and to disseminate the important message of sports and exercise in all social classes, Macau Sports Development Board organises on a monthly basis "Sports for All Day" in various social communities, in order to promote residents’ participation in sports and to achieve the goal of lifelong exercise. </p><p>Location: Terreno ao lado do Jardim da Cidade das Flores (Rua de Coimbra) from 16.00 to 18.30.</p>